with role    utility
with trait   gnome
with source    stable $GNOME_URL sources/mousetweaks/${VERSION:0:3}/mousetweaks-$VERSION.tar.xz
with source  unstable $GNOME_URL sources/mousetweaks/${VERSION:0:3}/mousetweaks-$VERSION.tar.xz
with info    last 20120929
with info    home http://live.gnome.org/Mousetweaks/Home
with info    cite 'accessibility enhancements for GNOME

From the README:

1. It offers a way to perform clicks without using the button.

2. It allows a right click
   by doing a click and hold of the left mouse button.

3. It provides an applet that can be installed on the panel.
   This applet creates an area on the panel
   into which the pointer can be captured
   until the user releases it
   with a predefined button and modifier combination.'
